  ### `blur`

  **Type:** `string`

  **Default:** `undefined`

  Blurs the image. When no argument is provided it performs a fast blur. When an argument between `0.3` and `1000` is provided it performs a more accurate gaussian blur.

  **Code example:**
</Markdown>

